00:00:26.069 --> 00:00:32.280
Now this right here is a creamy, sweet desert
style cocktail and it is the Toblerone Cocktail

00:00:32.280 --> 00:00:34.750
and this is how to make it.

00:00:34.750 --> 00:00:37.380
For this you will need
2 oz of Cream

00:00:37.380 --> 00:00:45.430
1 oz of Coffee Liqueur or Kahlua
1 oz of Baileys Irish Cream

00:00:45.430 --> 00:00:55.970
1 oz of Frangelico Hazelnut Liqueur
some Honey

00:00:55.970 --> 00:00:57.560
and Chocolate topping.

00:00:57.560 --> 00:01:03.780
In a cocktail shaker with ice pour in your
2 oz of cream.

00:01:03.780 --> 00:01:12.570
1 oz of Kahlua Coffee Liqueur
1 oz of Baileys Irish Cream

00:01:12.570 --> 00:01:21.640
1 oz of Frangelico Hazelnut Liqueur
put the lid on your cocktail shaker and give

00:01:21.640 --> 00:01:27.100
a good shake.

00:01:27.100 --> 00:01:43.350
To prepare your glass, drizzle chocolate topping
around the inside of your glass.

00:01:43.350 --> 00:01:49.110
Do the same with some honey.

00:01:49.110 --> 00:01:58.530
Fill your glass with ice cubes, and strain
your cocktail into the glass.

00:01:58.530 --> 00:02:05.180
And I present to you the Toblerone Cocktail.
Cheers

00:02:05.180 --> 00:02:13.529
It looks alot like a chocolate milk shake,
its very sweet chocolatey and creamy. If your

00:02:13.529 --> 00:02:18.319
