am I myself you actaully can't really taste

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:24.949
it. It tastes more like a Toblerone chocolate
bar, you can really taste the cream and frangelico

00:02:24.949 --> 00:02:27.149
and baileys more than you can anything else.

